b\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It can be in the abdominal.\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the abdominal\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 848}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It can be in the spine, in the ribs.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 886, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the spine\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 872}, {\"ngram\": \"the ribs\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 885}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it feels like if I point my feet, it will stay in it,\\\" Dion explained to Kotb.\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my feet\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"Dion\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 950}, {\"ngram\": \"Kotb\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Or if I cook, my fingers or my hands will get in position.\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1029, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my fingers\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 995}, {\"ngram\": \"my hands\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"position\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's cramping, but it's like you are in the position of you cannot unlock them.\\\"\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1110, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cramping\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"the position\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1082}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kotb did tease after their interview that Dion had plans to return to the stage for a live performance.\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1215, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kotb\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"their interview\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"Dion\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1158}, {\"ngram\": \"plans\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"the stage\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1191}, {\"ngram\": \"a live performance\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So when a caller asked the journalist what she knew about this potential appearance, Kotb spilled some tea onWWHL.\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1330, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a caller\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1232}, {\"ngram\": \"the journalist\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1253}, {\"ngram\": \"this potential appearance\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1299}, {\"ngram\": \"Kotb\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1305}, {\"ngram\": \"some tea onWWHL\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Her manager was off-camera, and I was like, 'So what's going on?\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1397, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her manager\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1344}, {\"ngram\": \"camera\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When are you performing again?'\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And she goes, 'Can I tell her?'\\\"\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1462, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kotb shared, adopting Dion's accent.\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1499, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kotb\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1467}, {\"ngram\": \"Dion's accent\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And her manager goes, 'No!'\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1528, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her manager\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He screams, 'No.'\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1546, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was like, there is something.\\\"\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The caller questioned whether that appearance might take place during the upcomingParis Olympics.\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The caller\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1591}, {\"ngram\": \"that appearance\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1626}, {\"ngra